summary: what jon doesnt get is that the northerners rather die than be oppressed by southerners who don’t understand, respect or care...
body: what jon doesnt get is that the northerners rather die than be oppressed by southerners who don’t understand, respect or care for them. his brother died because he refused to kneel to the lannisters at the behest of the northern lords. they dont WANT a southern king they want independence by any means necessary. so yeah the northerners are a bit prickly about letting outsiders control them after having their last four rulers, rickard, brandon, ned and robb murdered by southerners, two of them murdered by Targs. jon’s “kingdom” was never his to give away. he was elected and then he acts all surprised when no one wants to follow some pyromaniac lady targ who brought two fire monsters with her.
